messages.message:
getting `400 Bad Request` when I try to open a jupyter notebook on Instabase - am I doing anything wrong?

also want to know how/if I can run/import instabase modules in jupyter notebook?

If you check out utils.py under ipython folder I believe you'll see the methods which get imported under the ib namespace. E.g., ib.open, ib.list_dir, etc
